commitResults.messageTitle: Refactor commands in logic.command to reflect refactoring persons to trips
Refactor travelr to take store trips
commitResults.messageBody:
Travelr was storing persons, we want travelr to store trips as
that is what travelr is designed to do.

All traces of person are erased and replaced with the model trip
which contains a Title and a Description.

commitResults.messageTitle: Fix bug where save data is not loading
Fix a bug where the save data is not loading
commitResults.messageBody:
The loggers suggests that save data in json format is being read
but the trips are not being loaded into travelr.

JsonSerializableAddressBook#toModelType() reads the json file but
did not add the trips it read to travelr.

Add trip to travelr after converting trip from json using
toModelType()

commitResults.messageTitle: Add components package and add description class and title class
commitResults.messageBody:

but used by different classes (trips and events).

Extract the similar classes of the trips and events to improve code
quality.
